after each sentence

1. *Gospodaru*, molim te da mi pomogneš. (Lord, I beg you to help me.)
2. *Gospodara* je štitio od zla. (The lord shielded him from evil.)
3. Osećam da se *gospodaru* često odupire. (I feel like the lord is often defied.)
4. *Gospodar* je bio izuzetno blag i pravedan. (The lord was exceptionally kind and just.)
5. *Gospodaru*, molim te da mi omogućiš da učinim pravu stvar. (Lord, I beg you to let me do the right thing.)